'''美洲擬獅'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Panthera atrox''}}）又名'''擬獅'''或'''擬獅兽'''，是一種從[[化石|化石]]得知已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[貓科|貓科]][[動物|動物]]，生存於[[更新世|更新世]]時期的[[北美洲|北美洲]]（340,000 - 11,000 年前）<ref name=dinosaurs.about>{{cite web | last = Strauss | first = Bob | authorlink =  | title = American Lion (''Panthera leo atrox'') | work = About.Com Dinosaurs | publisher = [[The_New_York_Times_Company|The New York Times Company]] | url = http://dinosaurs.about.com/od/mesozoicmammals/p/American-Lion-Panthera-Leo-Atrox.htm | accessdate = 2012-03-10 | archive-date = 2016-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927040557/http://dinosaurs.about.com/od/mesozoicmammals/p/American-Lion-Panthera-Leo-Atrox.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。基因研究顯示牠是[[穴獅|穴獅]]的[[姐妹群|姐妹群]]<ref name=Barnett>{{Cite journal | last1 = Barnett | first1 = R. | last2 = Shapiro | first2 = B. | authorlink2 = Beth Shapiro | last3 = Barnes | first3 = I. A. N. | last4 = Ho | first4 = S. Y. W. | last5 = Burger | first5 = J. | authorlink5 = Joachim Burger | last6 = Yamaguchi | first6 = N. | last7 = Higham | first7 = T. F. G. | last8 = Wheeler | first8 = H. T. | last9 = Rosendahl | first9 = W. | last10 = Sher | first10 = A. V. | last11 = Sotnikova | first11 = M. | last12 = Kuznetsova | first12 = T. | last13 = Baryshnikov | first13 = G. F. | last14 = Martin | first14 = L. D. | last15 = Harington | first15 = C. R. | last16 = Burns | first16 = J. A. | last17 = Cooper | first17 = A. | title = Phylogeography of lions (''Panthera leo'' ssp.) reveals three distinct taxa and a late Pleistocene reduction in genetic diversity | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-294X.2009.04134.x | journal = Molecular Ecology | volume = 18 | issue = 8 | pages = 1668–1677 | year = 2009 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/24216045 | pmid = 19302360 | pmc =  | access-date = 2019-02-05 | archive-date = 2018-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180920011400/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/24216045 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，為[[更新世巨型動物群|更新世巨型動物群]]，化石主要發現於[[美國|美國]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[拉布雷亞瀝青坑|拉布雷亞瀝青坑]]。美洲擬獅體型與[[更新世|更新世]]中期的[[原始獅|原始獅]]大小相近，且比現今[[非洲|非洲]]的獅子大25%，為目前已知體型最大的貓科之一<ref name=SDNHM>{{Cite web|author=Dr. Tom Deméré|title=SDNHM Fossil Mysteries Field Guide:American Lion|publisher=San Diego Natural History Museum|url=http://www.sdnhm.org/exhibits/mystery/fg_lion.html|accessdate=2007-07-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625205421/http://www.sdnhm.org/exhibits/mystery/fg_lion.html|archivedate=2009-06-25}}</ref>。

== 分類學 ==
[[Image:Felis_atrox_jaw.jpg|thumb]]
美洲擬獅最早由美國古生物學家[[約瑟夫·萊迪|約瑟夫·萊迪]]於 1853 年以 ''Felis atrox'' 為名命名並進行發表<ref name="leidy1853">{{cite journal|last1= Leidy|first1= Joseph|author-link= Joseph Leidy|year= 1853|title= Description of an Extinct Species of American Lion: ''Felis atrox''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_transactions-of-the-american-philosophical-society_1853_10/page/n392|journal= Transactions of the American Philosophical Society|volume= 10|pages= 319–322|doi= 10.2307/1005282|jstor= 1005282|via=}}</ref>。Hemmer 於 1974 年提議將美洲擬獅以{{link-en|三名法|trinomen}}命名為 ''Panthera leo atrox''<ref name=hemmer1974>{{cite journal |last=Hemmer |first=H. |year=1974 |title=Untersuchungen zur Stammesgeschichte der Pantherkatzen (''Pantherinae''), Teil III: Zur Artgeschichte des Löwen ''Panthera'' (''Panthera'') ''leo'' (Linnaeus 1758) |journal=Veröffentlichungen der Zoologischen Staatssammlung München |volume=17 |issue= |pages=167–280 |url=https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/30061613 |access-date=2019-12-12 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517151818/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/30061613 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這項提議於 1985 年受到 {{link-en|Björn Kurten}}的支持<ref>{{cite journal|last1= Kurtén|first1= B.|author-link= Björn Kurtén|title= The Pleistocene lion of Beringia|jstor= 23734190|journal= Annales Zoologici Fennici|volume= 22|issue= 1|date= 1985|pages= 117–121|url= http://www.sekj.org/PDF/anzf22/anzf22-117-121.pdf|access-date= 2019-12-12|archive-date= 2020-07-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200726002159/http://www.sekj.org/PDF/anzf22/anzf22-117-121.pdf|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

美洲擬獅一開始被認為是[[豹亞科|豹亞科]]下獨立[[物種|物種]]，學名為 ''Panthera atrox'' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|p|æ|n|θ|ər|ə|_|ˈ|æ|t|r|ɒ|k|s}}，[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]意思是「兇殘的豹」。但是一部分的[[古生物學家|古生物學家]]認為美洲擬獅應為現存[[非洲獅|非洲獅]]及[[穴獅|穴獅]]的近親，而在之後將美洲擬獅命名為 ''P. leo atrox''，列為非洲獅的亞種而非獨立物種<ref name= "Christiansen2009">{{cite journal |last1=Christiansen|first1= P.|last2= Harris|first2=J. M.|title= Craniomandibular morphology and phylogenetic affinities of ''Panthera atrox'': implications for the evolution and paleobiology of the lion lineage |year=2009 |journal= Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology |volume=29 |issue=3 |pages= 934−945|doi= 10.1671/039.029.0314}}</ref>。近年來，美洲擬獅與穴獅則再次被視為是獨立物種<ref name=Barnett2016>{{cite journal |last1=Barnett |first1=R. |last2=Mendoza |first2=M. L. Z. |last3=Soares |first3=A. E. R. |last4=Ho |first4=S. Y. W. |last5=Zazula |first5=G. |last6=Yamaguchi |first6=N. |last7=Shapiro |first7=B. |last8=Kirillova |first8=I. V. |last9=Larson |first9=G. |last10=Gilbert |first10=M. T. P. |title=Mitogenomics of the Extinct Cave Lion, ''Panthera spelaea'' (Goldfuss, 1810), Resolve its Position within the ''Panthera'' Cats |journal=Open Quaternary |volume=2 |year=2016 |page=4 |doi=10.5334/oq.24 |url=http://www.openquaternary.com/jms/article/download/oq.24/31 |access-date=2019-12-12 |archive-date=2018-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180721161709/https://www.openquaternary.com/jms/article/download/oq.24/31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==描述==
[[Image:Panthera_atrox.jpg|thumb]][[拉布雷亞瀝青坑#喬治·C·佩奇博物館|喬治·C·佩奇博物館]]]] 
[[Image:Panthera_Atrox.jpg|thumb]]]]
美洲擬獅的體長（不含尾巴）估計為 {{convert|1.6|to|2.5|m|abbr=on}}<ref name="Quaternary extinctions">{{Citation | last = Anderson | first = Elaine | author-link = Elaine Anderson | chapter = Who's Who in the Pleistocene: A Mammalian Bestiary | chapterurl = http://google.com/books?id=qIDC7ybvHQEC&pg=PA59 | editor-last = Martin | editor-first = P. S. | editor-link = Paul S. Martin | editor2-last = Klein | editor2-first = R. G. | editor2-link = Richard Klein (paleoanthropologist) | title = Quaternary Extinctions | publisher = [[The_University_of_Arizona_Press|The University of Arizona Press]] | year = 1984 | isbn = 978-0-8165-1100-6 | url = http://google.com/books?id=qIDC7ybvHQEC&printsec=frontcover | accessdate = 2019-02-05 | archive-date = 2014-12-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229192528/http://google.com/books?id=qIDC7ybvHQEC&printsec=frontcover | dead-url = no }}</ref>，肩高則為 {{Convert|1.2|m|ft|1|abbr=on}}，可比牠的近親[[原始獅|原始獅]]，且大於[[斯劍虎|斯劍虎]]（體重可達 {{Convert|280|kg|lb|abbr=on}}），但仍小於同期體型最大的[[短面熊|短面熊]]（當時北美洲體型最大的[[食肉目|食肉目]]）.<ref name = "Christiansen">{{cite journal | last = Christiansen | first = P. | authorlink = |author2=Harris, J. M. | title = Body size of ''Smilodon'' (Mammalia: Felidae) | journal = [[Journal_of_Morphology|Journal of Morphology]] | volume = 266 | issue = 3| pages = 369–384 | date = 2005-10-18 | language = | jstor = | doi = 10.1002/jmor.10384 | pmid=16235255}}</ref>。一項 2008 年的研究認為美洲擬獅的體重可達 {{Convert|420|kg|lbs|abbr=on}}<ref>{{Cite journal | last = Sorkin | first = B. | authorlink = | title = A biomechanical constraint on body mass in terrestrial mammalian predators | journal = [[Lethaia|Lethaia]] | volume = 41 | issue = 4 | pages = 333–347 | date = 2008-04-10 | language = | doi = 10.1111/j.1502-3931.2007.00091.x }}</ref><ref>[[John_Campbell_Merriam|Merriam, J. C.]] & Stock, C. 1932: The Felidae of Rancho La Brea. Carnegie Institution of Washington Publications 442, 1–231.</ref>。一項 2009 年針對最大體型樣本的研究則認為雌獅的體重平均為 {{convert|256|kg|lbs|abbr=on}}，雄獅則為 {{convert|351|kg|lbs|abbr=on}}<ref name="Christiansen & Harris 2009">{{Cite journal |last=Christiansen |first=Per |last2=Harris |first2=John M. |year=2009 |title=Craniomandibular Morphology and Phylogenetic Affinities of ''Panthera atrox'': Implications for the Evolution and Paleobiology of the Lion Lineage |journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology |volume=29 |issue=3 |pages=934–945 |doi=10.1671/039.029.0314}}</ref>。一項 2008 年的研究預估雄獅的體重為 {{convert|235|-|523|kg|lb|abbr=in}}，雌獅為 {{convert|175|-|365|kg|lb|abbr=in}}，高於斯劍虎<ref name="DeSantisetal.,2012">{{cite journal|author1=DeSantis, L. R. |author2=Schubert, B. W. |author3=Scott, J. R. |author4=Ungar, P. S. |title=Implications of diet for the extinction of saber-toothed cats and American lions |journal=PLoS ONE |volume=7 |issue=12 |pages=e52453 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0052453 |pmid=23300674 |pmc=3530457 |year=2012 |bibcode=2012PLoSO...752453D}}</ref>。

在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]][[拉布雷亞瀝青坑|拉布雷亞瀝青坑]]中已發現約有80個美洲擬獅標本，故此對牠有較多資料<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://nhm.org/site/research-collections/rancho-la-brea/about-rlb-mammals|title=About Rancho La Brea Mammals|date=2012-08-06|website=Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County|access-date=2017-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028201119/https://nhm.org/site/research-collections/rancho-la-brea/about-rlb-mammals|archive-date=2017-10-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。美洲擬獅的特徵及[[牙齒|牙齒]]非常像現今的[[獅子|獅子]]，但體型較大。

發現於[[巴塔哥尼亞|巴塔哥尼亞]][[阿根廷|阿根廷]]地區洞穴裡的美洲擬獅遺骸尚保有部分皮膚殘骸，從這些皮膚樣本上可以知道美洲擬獅具有偏紅的體色，而阿根廷[[聖克魯斯省_(阿根廷)|聖克魯斯省]]聖龐沙的[[石洞壁畫|石洞壁畫]]也證實了這點。體色的差異有助於科學家區別美洲擬獅與美洲豹的遺骸，因為在壁畫中美洲豹被描述為具有偏黃的體色<ref>{{cite web|title=Revelan que el León Americano Habitó la Patagonia|language=es|trans-title=They Reveal that the American Lion Inhabited Patagonia|url=https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=es&u=http://www.todociencia.com.ar/revelan-que-el-leon-americano-habito-la-patagonia/|website=Todo Ciencia|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2001-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011020223533/http://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Chimento2017"/>。

==分佈==
美洲擬獅在[[更新世|更新世]]最先出現於[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]南部（[[桑加蒙間冰期|桑加蒙間冰期]]，為最後一次的[[間冰期|間冰期]]），並散佈至[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]與[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]，最南可至[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Marisol Montellano | first1 = Ballesteros | last2 = Carbot-Chanona | first2 = Gerardo | title = ''Panthera leo atrox'' (Mammalia: Carnivora: Felidae) in Chiapas, Mexico | url = https://chiapas.academia.edu/GerardoCarbotChanona/Papers/1033452/Panthera_leo_atrox_Mammalia_Carnivora_Felidae_in_Chiapas_Mexico | journal = The Southwestern Naturalist | volume = 54 | issue = 2| pages = 217–222 | doi=10.1894/clg-20.1| year = 2009 }}</ref>，北美洲中只有[[加拿大東部|加拿大東部]]及[[美國東北部|美國東北部]]不見其蹤影，可能因為當時當地環境為[[北方針葉林|北方針葉林]]的關係<ref name="Quaternary extinctions" /><ref name="Database">{{cite web|url=http://fossilworks.org/bridge.pl?a=taxonInfo&taxon_no=162281|title=''Panthera leo atrox''|last=|first=|date=|work=[[Paleobiology_Database|Paleobiology Database]]|publisher=|format=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216194132/http://fossilworks.org/bridge.pl?a=taxonInfo&taxon_no=162281|archive-date=2016-02-16|dead-url=no|accessdate=2012-03-11}}</ref><ref name="Harrington1996">{{Cite web|url=http://www.tc.gov.yk.ca/publications/Lion_1996.pdf|title=American Lion|last=Harrington|first=C. R.|date=March 1996|website=[[Yukon_Beringia_Interpretive_Centre|Yukon Beringia Interpretive Centre]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030054134/http://www.tc.gov.yk.ca/publications/Lion_1996.pdf|archive-date=2017-10-30|dead-url=|access-date=2017-10-30}}</ref>。原先美洲擬獅被認為在[[南北美洲生物大遷徙|南北美洲生物大遷徙]]時擴展至[[南美洲|南美洲]]東北部<ref name="Kurtén1980">{{cite book|last1= Kurtén|first1= B.|last2= Anderson|first2= E.|title= Pleistocene Mammals of North America|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=nBWVngEACAAJ|year= 1980|publisher= Columbia University Press|isbn= 978-0231037334|oclc= 759120597}}</ref>，然而[[祕魯|祕魯]][[塔拉拉|塔拉拉]]瀝青坑發現的化石其實屬於一種大型的[[美洲豹|美洲豹]]<ref name="Seymour1983">{{Cite thesis |last=Seymour |first=Kevin L. |title=The Felinae (Mammalia: Felidae) from the Late Pleistocene tar seeps at Talara, Peru, with a critical examination of the fossil and recent felines of North and South America |date=1983 |degree=MSc |publisher=University of Toronto}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Seymour |first=Kevin L. |date=2015 |title=Perusing Talara: Overview of the Late Pleistocene fossils from the tar seeps of Peru |url=http://www.tarpits.org/sites/default/files/pdfs/Scott%20et%20al%202015.%20LACM%20SS%2042.pdf#page=107 |journal=Science Series |volume=42 |pages=97–109 |author= |access-date=2019-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001080809/http://www.tarpits.org/sites/default/files/pdfs/Scott%20et%20al%202015.%20LACM%20SS%2042.pdf#page=107 |archive-date=2018-10-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Yamaguchi2004">{{Cite journal | last1 = Yamaguchi | first1 = N. | last2 = Cooper | first2 = A. | last3 = Werdelin | first3 = L. | last4 = MacDonald | first4 = D. W. | title = Evolution of the mane and group-living in the lion (Panthera leo): A review | doi = 10.1017/S0952836904005242 | journal = Journal of Zoology | volume = 263 | issue = 4 | pages = 329 | year = 2004 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>不過另一方面在[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]及[[智利|智利]]南部發現的化石，原先屬於已絕種的美洲豹亞種 ''Panthera onca mesembrina'' ，現在則認為屬於美洲擬獅<ref name = "Chimento2017">{{Cite journal|last1= Chimento|first1= N. R.|last2= Agnolin|first2=F. L.|year= 2017 |title= The fossil American lion (''Panthera atrox'') in South America: Palaeobiogeographical implications |journal= Comptes Rendus Palevol |volume= 16|issue= 8|pages= 850–864|doi= 10.1016/j.crpv.2017.06.009}}</ref>。就像其他巨大的[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]，牠於約1萬年前的更新世末[[滅絕|滅絕]]。美洲擬獅的遺骸在[[育空|育空]]及[[拉布雷亞瀝青坑|拉布雷亞瀝青坑]]中非常普遍。

==生活環境==
美洲擬獅和現代[[獅子|獅子]]一樣生活在[[疏林草原|疏林草原]]和[[草原|草原]]<ref name="SDNHM" />，一些美洲擬獅是生活在冰冷的[[氣候|氣候]]環境。牠們有可能生活於[[洞穴|洞穴]]中或岩縫間，以躲避冰冷的天氣<ref name="Harrington1996" />。牠們可能以草或樹葉鋪巢，就像[[東北虎|東北虎]]般<ref name="Harrington1996" />。

美洲擬獅在[[拉布雷亞瀝青坑|拉布雷亞瀝青坑]]中的數量較[[斯劍虎|斯劍虎]]或[[恐狼|恐狼]]為少，相信牠們比劍齒虎更有智慧避開陷阱<ref name=SDNHM/>，或不是獵食坑中獵物。美洲擬獅似乎是獵食[[鹿|鹿]]、{{link-en|史氏馬|Equus scotti}}、[[駱駝|駱駝]]、[[加州貘|加州貘]]、[[美洲野牛|美洲野牛]]、[[猛獁象|猛獁象]]及其他巨型的[[草食性|草食性]][[有蹄類|有蹄類]]<ref name="Christiansen & Harris 2009" /><ref name="Harrington1996" />。

美洲擬獅的[[滅絕|滅絕]]與[[全新世滅絕事件|全新世滅絕事件]]有關。牠們的骨頭可以在[[舊石器時代|舊石器時代]][[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]的垃圾中發現，所以被[[人類|人類]]獵殺有可能是成因之一<ref name="Quaternary extinctions"/><ref name="Harrington1996" />。

美洲擬獅的第一個標本是一個[[顎骨|顎骨]]，其複製品現正擺放在{{link-en|費城自然科學學院|Academy of Natural Sciences of Drexel University}}的[[約瑟夫·萊迪|約瑟夫·萊迪]]（Joseph Leidy）雕像之下。

==分類==
美洲擬獅被認為是[[獅|獅]]的[[亞種|亞種]]，但有的認為本身是一個[[種|種]]。在比較[[頭顱骨|頭顱骨]]後，有指[[穴獅|穴獅]]較美洲擬獅更為接近[[老虎|老虎]]<ref name=Groiss1996>{{Cite journal en|author=Groiss, J.Th.|year=1996|title=Der Hohlentiger ''Panthera tigris spelaea'' (Goldfuss)|journal=Neves Jahrb. Geol. Palaont. Abh.|volume=7|pages=399-414}}</ref>，但是[[基因|基因]]研究結果指美洲擬獅與現今[[獅子|獅子]]有更接近的基因關係。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Burger, Joachim ''et al.''|year=2004|title=Molecular phylogeny of the extinct cave lion ''Panthera leo spelaea''|journal=Mol. Phylogenet. Evol.|volume=30|pages=841-849|url=http://www.uni-mainz.de/FB/Biologie/Anthropologie/MolA/Download/Burger%202004.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070925204424/http://www.uni-mainz.de/FB/Biologie/Anthropologie/MolA/Download/Burger%202004.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-25}}</ref>

